records.name: Ostrov Palm

descriptions.direction: Located in Ukulhas, Ostrov Palm Villa is near the airport and on the waterfront. Folhudhoo Harbor and Ukulhas Harbor are local landmarks, and the area's natural beauty can be seen at Ari Atoll and Ukulhas Beach.
descriptions.general: Close to Ukulhas Beach, Ostrov Palm is located in Ukulhas and has wellness packages and garden. This 3-star guest house offers a spa experience, with its hot tub and spa facilities. The accommodation provides free WiFi throughout the property, as well as a terrace and a family-friendly restaurant.
descriptions.other: This property will not accommodate hen, stag or similar parties.
